Package com.example.networkmeup.domain

Class TINTest

java.lang.Object
com.example.networkmeup.domain.TINTest
public class TINTest extends Object
TINTest class contains unit tests for validating the TIN (Tax Identification Number) class functionality. These tests check various scenarios related to setting and validating TIN numbers.
